  "description": "The MikroTik QuickMOUNT X (QM-X) is a durable and versatile mounting adapter designed to provide flexible installation options for SXTsq series devices. It allows you to easily attach MikroTik’s SXTsq models to poles, ensuring secure and stable placement. The adapter supports both vertical and horizontal adjustments, offering precise alignment with fine-tuning up to 140° in both axes. This level of flexibility makes it possible to achieve the best possible signal quality and link stability, which is especially important in long-distance wireless connections. The QuickMOUNT X is made of strong reinforced plastic, ensuring long-lasting durability in both indoor and outdoor environments. Specifically designed for SXTsq devices, it is ideal for wireless ISPs, network installers, or advanced home users, providing a reliable and cost-effective solution for mounting antennas at offices, industrial facilities, remote sites, or residential properties.",
